Class Scan

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swinburne.irtsa.irtsa.model.Scan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Scan
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Scan model object to represent a saved scan. Implements Parcelable so a Scan can be added to a bundle and easily passed between Fragments/Activities.
